summary: The file defines a specialized ONNX-based Stable Diffusion pipeline that supports long prompts with weighted terms, enabling advanced text-to-image generation capabilities. It includes utilities for parsing prompts, handling token weights, and preprocessing images and masks, while providing methods for image generation, image-to-image translation, and inpainting.
business_intent: To provide a flexible and efficient solution for generating high-quality images from detailed, weighted textual descriptions, catering to creative industries, marketing, and product visualization needs.
